From: Ray Liu <ray.xy.liu@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] pinctrl: airoha: add support for AN7563 pins

Add AN7563-specific pin, group, function and pin configuration data to
the shared Airoha pinctrl driver. AN7563 shares the EN7581 register
layout but exposes a smaller pad set and uses extra GPIO mux bits for
the standalone PCIe reset, I2C, SPI and UART pads.

Signed-off-by: Ray Liu <ray.xy.liu@gmail.com>
